      <title>澳大利亚巨型基金控制着 9 万亿美元的养老金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/australian-mega-funds-seen-controlling-9-trillion-of-pensions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[未来几十年，随着不断增加的合并和竞争只剩下少数强大的投资者，一群庞大的养老基金将主导澳大利亚的退休体系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/australian-mega-funds-seen-controlling-9-trillion-of-pensions</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 00:31:20 GMT</pubDate>
